plugin:
  figure out why you don't get to modify window.X or document.X in the
    tipsy_parser.js code

  To get the resizing of the sidebar to work:
  The following CSS code must be included in the userChrome.css inside the chrome dir of the firefox user profile:
@namespace url("http://www.mozilla.org/keymaster/gatekeeper/there.is.only.xul"); /* set default namespace to XUL */

#sidebar {max-width: none !important; }

  Find out if there is anyway we can change this css file from within the plugin.

